summary:
A construction project manager with 20 years of fit-out life-cycle experience on three continents and numerous countries and cultures. My current focus is on integrated corporate real estate, labs and clean rooms, AI, AR, IOT, and end user experience.

Today's venn diagram of me intersects at: 
"love the challenge"/ "OCD kicking in"/ "sorry...I thought we moved on?"

Professionally, my bosses are in the following order:
1) Daughter
2) Client
3) Line Manager

Communication is key... always open to it, so feel free to reach out.
